{"id": 1426, "genre": 1000, "title": "你都看烦了哪些虚伪的前缀？", "description": "微电影和大电影都不是电影；轻小说和微小说都不能算是小说。本来挺好的东西，加了个前缀就完全不是原来的意思了呢。（题图来自：Yukai Du）", "record_count": 19987, "comment_count": 33, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170104000444YIuKWojgZdmBn4iN.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-01-04T17:00:29Z", "questions": [{"id": 1642, "title": "你都看烦了哪些虚伪的前缀？", "content": "你都看烦了哪些虚伪的前缀？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 150261, "content": " “新”中式，家里摆个博古架的所谓新中式", "image": "img/option/option/20170103232304k87bJ69uCmUqBMWF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 150262, "content": "“轻”断食，三天吃草两天火锅一切归零", "image": "img/option/option/20170103232459D4a6tjP8Xyv2UNIm.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 150264, "content": "“轻”奢，即，用起来会获得轻视的低阶奢侈品", "image": "img/option/option/20170103232641xXikJ7NVSwHBtKfA.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 150265, "content": " “轻”阅读，今年一共读了三本书，两本半是时尚杂志", "image": "img/option/option/20170103232949kyNFvVqP3xjI2Mu9.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 150267, "content": "“轻”喜剧，大多数都不好笑，还有点无聊", "image": "img/option/option/2017010323340061K4lbfHkphdXIOt.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 150269, "content": "“大”电影，除了长度也没啥别的电影元素了", "image": "img/option/option/20170103233831mXeaRYzcvo3gCIql.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 150268, "content": "“微”电影，就叫视频短片能怎样？", "image": "img/option/option/20170103233815gzmcH1ReL0EZU4YA.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 150273, "content": "“微”课，效率低下且主要用于勾搭的线上长江商学院", "image": "img/option/option/20170103234535q6G1Rlt7YeP2hgo0.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 150278, "content": "“裸”妆，费劲巴拉画一个像是没化妆的妆", "image": "img/option/option/20170103235218L1FVPrpsKnW3NDqa.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 150282, "content": " “泛”娱乐生态，即，一个IP四处圈钱的业界生态", "image": "img/option/option/20170103235353uHeU5pCivoRx7OMr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}